text: Neville Hunte (born 5 August 1948) is a former Guyanese cyclist. He competed in the sprint and 1000m time trial events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Guyanese male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Guyana Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Guyana Category:Cyclists at the 1970 British Commonwealth Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
